description: A midnight swim brings about a revelation for Chopstick, as repressed memories and feelings rise to the surface. The skinheads make their move, and Tracy's fate hangs in the balance!

Doctor Who Magazine Special: The Music of Doctor Who

In the 1960s, Doctor Who’s bold use of avant-garde music and sound design played just as important a role as visual effects in evoking a journey through time and space. This is the story of those radiophonic pioneers and the composers who built on their extraordinary legacy. Unprecedented in its scope and detail, The Music of Doctor Who explores one of the most celebrated and mysterious sonic landscapes in television history.
name: The Music of Doctor Who

description: Serialized from the pages of Dungeon Quest Book Three by Joe Daly, the band of weirdo warriors battles the mighty steam golem to save Nerdgirl. Will they survive and, more importantly, get their missing gear (and drugs) back?

Chapter Two: Night Flight

Under the guise of night, Hank sets out in a post-EMP world to save his family as civilization continues to deteriorate. Violence and deceit face him on the road to Rocky Ford. Hope hangs by a thread as he races time, starvation, and a world desperately clinging to survival.
name: Chapter Two: Night Flight

description:
Treasure Hunt

This month's comic continues the storyline launched last month as Miss Match, Elastic Man, Amazing Amazon and Mr. Fabulous are captured and transported to an organizer of exotic big-game hunting expeditions - and they're the prey! Can they quit arguing amongst themselves long enough to stay alive?
name: The Big Hunt Part 2: Treasure Hunt

description:
Uprising of Online Poker

It's November and the final 9 players are returning back to Las Vegas, they are joined with their family and friends who are there to support them. What do the players do a night before they sit down to compete in the biggest tournament of their life?!!!
name: Uprising of Online Poker

description: The Risen - Chapter 3: The dead are spreading faster than Holden and Grey can contain. The only hope for Cornerstone lies in uncovering the truth behind the outbreak and stopping it at its source, but that could prove more dangerous than facing an army of the dead. Don't miss the pulse pounding conclusion to 'The Risen'!
name: The Risen Chapter Three

description:
Lights... Camera... Aliens!

Bobby, Albert, and Iris are The Inquiring Minds, three kids who seek fun and adventure by exploring all things strange and unusual in their hometown of Three Craters Lake.

When strange lights are reported near Anderson Ridge, Albert is convinced that it's aliens from outer space. Bobby and Iris are convinced that they'll never get any homework done unless The Inquiring Minds investigate!

Will they find space aliens, or something even more unexpected?

Find out in... "Lights, Camera... Aliens!!"
name: Lights... Camera... Aliens!

description:
A TALE OF TWO DEATHS!

MEGA-CITY ONE – A NIGHTMARISH ENCLOSURE LOCATED ALONG THE EASTERN SEABOARD OF NORTH AMERICA. Only the Judges – powerful law enforcers supporting the despotic Justice Department – can stop total anarchy running rife on the crime-ridden streets. Toughest of them all is Judge Dredd – he is the law and these are his stories...

Judge Death and his foul cadre of henchmen, The Dark Judges, escape custody, forcing Dredd to follow them back to Deadworld, where he has to confront not one, but two versions of the evil superfiend! And one of the most illustrious Chief Judges finally meet their end out in the harsh wilderness known as the Cursed Earth.

With stories by Judge Dredd co-creator John Wagner (Strontium Dog) and art from such luminaries as Trevor Hairsine (Captain America) and Greg Staples (Dark Justice), Case Files 25 is essential reading!

THIS VOLUME INCLUDES THE STORIES FROM: 2000 AD Progs 984-1028 AND THE Judge Dredd Megazine Issues 3.16-3.18

PLUS!

  • Creator Bios
  • Gallery
name: Volume 25

volume.name: Judge Dredd The Complete Case Files

description: Fidel Castro’s lover makes a deal in America to kill Castro but follows it up with a mistake in Cuba before she can complete her task. JFK approves project MK-ULTRA and opens the door for the CIA to begin their mind alternating experiments. Speical Agent Bob makes it into Cuba and manages to break into Castro’s headquarters!

Homework

Secret's are spilling out every which way. The demon from Julius' past has come to visit Sergio. King Nilus has a kingdom to rule, but why exactly is a 12-year-old the one in charge? Everywhere's secret identity might not be entirely secret anymore, and Abigail, Bianca, Jet and Quinton's fun night out singing takes a serous downturn.
name: Homework

description:
Music-obsessed teens struggle through the rise and Fall of Generation X and the Alternative Rock era of the 1990s. They learn that the bonds of friendship they thought were unbreakable have already begun to crack, and the music they thought they'd love forever has already started to fade.

Note: The digital edition (8/12/2015) for this issue was released before the print edition.
After Scorpion and Havik disappear, all hell breaks loose inside the the throne room! Can Takeda, D'Vorah and the rest of the outworld crew stand against so many champions possesed by blood magik?
name: Blood Island Chapter 33: Deliverance

description:
The Tragic Tale of StrangeBlob NoPants

What with making his monthly sales quotas and homeschooling his kids, Pewfell's life is no longer his own. Could popular children's entertainer Strangeblob NoPants be the answer to all his problems?
name: The Tragic Tale of StrangeBlob NoPants

description:
Quote the Raven

The metropolis of Cog has become a battlefield. Werewolves, zombies, as The Morrigan--a looming three-faced goddess of death and battle--prepares for materialization on the physical plane. Corvan must gather his allies for this final stand. Sacrifices must be made. The ultimate plan must come together if there's any chance to save everyone in Cog Town and beyond!
name: Quote the Raven

description: The shadow war between Hydra and Leviathan has left a trail of destruction across the globe, and it's up to Nick Fury and his Secret Warriors to take them both out. Fury recruits the Howling Commandos, but will this reunion be the Howlers' last? Now, Fury must make some of the grittiest life-and-death choices his Warriors have ever seen. What is his final wild card, and how deep does his complex and dangerous scheme go? Plus: How does S.H.I.E.L.D. fit in with the Brotherhood of the Shield? Nick Fury and Baron Strucker face each other in a final showdown decades in the making - but what will their deaths mean to the Brotherhood's master plan? Jonathan Hickman's tale of intrigue and international espionage reaches its jaw-dropping climax here! Collecting SECRET WARRIORS #17-28 and SIEGE: SECRET WARRIORS #1.
name: Volume 2

description: Abducted and held captive on the planet, Alteria, the SENTINELS are separated between male and female members. Each group struggles to survive and re-unite with the other. Will the Kagaran prisoners be the allies they need? Will Splash, the only member able to escape, come to their rescue? Or will Serpenta, the new Queen of Alteria, lead them back to Earth?

Mysterious forests that appear out of nowhere? Check. Stampeding rhinorillas. Yep. A mythical Diver With A Skeleton Face? Uh-huh. Sam's found just about all the excitement she's ever dreamed of in this strange new world, but she just might be looking for something more than adventure...Enticing enough or missing something?
Translates What If? Civil War, What If? Secret Invasion, What If the Runaways Became the Young Avengers.

description: In The Beats: A Graphic History, those who were mad to live come back to life through artwork as pulsatingly vibrant as the movement itself. Told by Harvey Pekar and his frequent artistic collaborator Ed Piskor, and by a range of artists and writers, including feminist comic creator Trina Robbins and MAD Magazine artist Peter Kuper, The Beats takes us on a wild tour. From the Benzedrine-fueled antics of Kerouac, Ginsberg, and Burroughs to the painting sessions of Jay DeFeo's disheveled studio, from the jazz hipsters to beatnik chicks, from Chicago's beatnik bistro to San Francisco's famed City Lights bookstore, we see the storied era in all its incarnations.
name: HC/SC

As Mallow Man has a dream slash flashback of an old enemy, a threat to the world is growing in power (and not just the power in their pants.) ZING!

While Mallow Man and Bacon boy are hot on the job against the delicious SUSHI SQUAD, two old friends show up to help/recruit/guilt Mallow Man back into service. What could they possibly say to convince him to help… well i’m not gonna just tell you.. MUHAHA…read the book!

In an attempt to save Mallow Man’s old partner, he and his new under appreciated partner will risk their lives and shoot lots of things. Can they stand up against Dr. Microns evil army of Hot Dog Ninjas?

Mallow Man wakes up in the middle of a bad situation and we're not talking about a one night stand! Locked up in the dungeon of an evil mastermind, Mallow Man must escape with his team. How can Mallow Man save his old partner if he can&'t even save himself? and oh yeah… someone will die! Actually lots of people will die but someone important to the plot will die too!

36 pages of story arc finale amazingnessism is now available! Mallow Man is on his own fighting the master mind behind the disappearing agents. Let see how many stupid jokes I can cram into one fight scene!

Join Mallow Man and his sidekick Bacon Boy in their first over-dramatic story arc!

In a world of animated food products, poorly referenced art, and bad jokes, only one marshmallow stands in the way of world domination.
name: TPB

volume.name: Mallow Man: The Sweet Taste of Justice

description:
Agent Jett Slash

Zombies! (sigh)... Really? Again?

Perhaps Agent Jett Slash can finally put the genre out of it's misery... But don't count on it.

Atom Wakes, is a ten year old boy who gets plunged into an unwanted hell after losing all he held dear. Surviving nuke attacks, brushing with certain death, and hiding from a tyrannical leader, all while trying figure out the reasons and motives of a failed alien experiment that had left him with unimaginable powers.
name: Volume 1: Zeroed

description: Julie looks after her late older sister's son, Josh. One rainy day, she hurries home from work when a rather tall man with an exotic face appears in front of her. "My name is Rocco Leopardi, and I'd like to talk to you about your nephew," he says. Julie had heard about him from her sister. This man was a relative of Josh's father. He tells her that he would like the child to undergo a DNA test back in Sicily. Scared of losing her beloved nephew, and having a hard time fighting back Rocco's charms, Julie agrees to go with her nephew and Rocco to Sicily...
name: Vol. 1

volume.name: Captive at the Sicilian Billionaire's Command

description: Baby monsters are not good at staying put, the Center for Otherworld Science could have higher workplace safety standards, and Mags learns how to grieve for someone she never really liked.
Collected edition of self-published series 'Charlatan Tales', containing self-contained stories ranging from slice of life to the supernatural to psychedelic sci-fi.

Costumed vigilante Courage comes out of retirement after years of being inactive after being defeated by the villain Volatile. How will his old friends and foes react to his sudden reappearance? Will he be greeted with open arms...or clenched fists?

volume.name: Courage: The Eye of the Hurricane

description: The Northwood and Freemont kingdoms have been at war for a thousand years, a war that has claimed millions of lives. With Freemont at the brink of final defeat, a desperate leader makes a deal with a local vampire lord for help. A deal that soon backfires and results in an outbreak of vampyrism which suddenly threatens the the integrity of both societies. Faced with a common enemy, the two kingdoms finally unite lead by Northwood's valiant General Richard Bennett, and begin the long quest to rid their land of the dreaded disease, a task that might unearth a long hidden conspiracy between some leaders within their nation.
name: Vol. 1

description: Nonsensical, upside down craziness! It is a place where the ordinary can become extraordinary, and children's dreams become reality with humorous and endearing results. Little children and whimsical characters play and interact with each other in a fantastical realm. Tag along with Zoey, the cutest girl in school and messy hair Elliott as they run amok with their friends the Frog King, the devious Koala Bear, and a gang of penguins who call themselves the AnkleBiters.
name: Vol. 1

description:
A Hero is Born!

This one shot features the adventures of Dartman as he tries to bring to justice The Springer, who murdered and innocent man and save the lives of two hostages. All this action is brought to you by creator Richard D. Irving and art by Lee Melton and Bobby Penafiel. Features a cover by Dan Solano.
name: A Hero is Born!
